{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-56","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 56","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Forme često koriste polja za višestruki izbor za pitanja koja mogu imati više od jednog odgovora. Element <code>input</code> sa svojstvom elementa <code>type</code> postavljeno na <code>checkbox</code> stvara polje za višestruki izbor.</p>\n<p>Ispod elementa od <code>legend</code> koji ste postavili, dodajte <code>input</code> sa atributom elementa <code>type</code> koji je postavljen na <code>checkbox</code> i čiji tekst je:</p>\n<p><code> Loving</code></p>\n</section>","id":"5ef9b03c81a63668521804e2","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-56"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>Is your cat an indoor or outdoor cat?</legend>\n            <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"indoor\"> Indoor</label>\n            <label><input id=\"outdoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>What's your cat's personality?</legend>\n            \n          </fieldset>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[42,45],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Komponenta za <code>input</code> za vaš padajući okvir treba da ima etiketu za otvaranje, ali ne i etiketu za zatvaranje.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('fieldset > input') && !code.match(/<\\/input\\>/g));"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo je da dodate samo jedno polje za unos u svoj okvir za izbor. Uklonite sve suvišnosti.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(document.querySelectorAll('fieldset > input'), 1);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoja nova sekcija <code>input</code> treba da bude ispod sekcije <code>legend</code> sa tekstom <code>What's your cat's personality?</code>. Postavila si je u pogređem redosledu.</p>","testString":"const existingLegendElem = document.querySelectorAll('fieldset > legend')?.[1];\nassert.strictEqual(\n  existingLegendElem?.nextElementSibling?.nodeName,\n  'INPUT'\n);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj novi element <code>input</code> nema svojstvo elementa <code>type</code>. Proveri da postoji razmak nakon imena oznake za otvaranje.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('fieldset > input')?.hasAttribute('type'));"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj novi element za <code>input</code> treba da ima atribut elementa <code>type</code> sa vrednošću <code>checkbox</code>. Izostavili ste vrednost ili ste napravili greške u kucanju. Zapamtite da vrednosti atributa elementa moraju biti okružene navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert.match(document.querySelector('fieldset > input')?.getAttribute('type'),/^checkbox$/i);"},{"text":"<p>Iako ste postavili atribut elementa <code>input</code> novog elementa <code>type</code> da bude <code>checkbox</code>, savetuje se uvek izvlačenje vrednosti atributa elementa i navodnika.</p>","testString":"assert(!/\\<\\s*input\\s+type\\s*=\\s*checkbox/i.test(code));"},{"text":"<p>Tekst <code> Loving</code> treba da bude postavljen direktno sa desne strane vašeg padajućeg menija. Proverite da postoji razmak između elementa i teksta. Ostavili ste tekst ili ste napravili pravopisne greške.</p>","testString":"const checkboxInputElem = document.querySelector('input[type=\"checkbox\"]');\nassert.match(\n  checkboxInputElem?.nextSibling?.nodeValue?.replace(/\\s+/g, ' '),\n  / Loving/i\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/#learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-56","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-57","prevChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-55","id":"5ef9b03c81a63668521804e2","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>Is your cat an indoor or outdoor cat?</legend>\n            <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"indoor\" checked> Indoor</label>\n            <label><input id=\"outdoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>What's your cat's personality?</legend>\n            <label for=\"loving\"><input id=\"loving\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"loving\" checked> Loving</label>\n            <label for=\"lazy\"><input id=\"lazy\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"lazy\"> Lazy</label>\n            <label for=\"energetic\"><input id=\"energetic\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"energetic\"> Energetic</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-56"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}